oj3E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “ANMC”是根据冈和秀所描绘的故事和世界观制作音乐和独立游戏的项目，来自神椿工作室内外的多位艺术家参与了歌曲。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.96wp3wjqm67o-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.96wp3wjqm67o-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.96wp3wjqm67o-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.96wp3wjqm67o-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.96wp3wjqm67o-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.275te66p6p6j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.275te66p6p6j-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.275te66p6p6j-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.275te66p6p6j-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.275te66p6p6j-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.5b3dpx8k4cq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/53ee52ad54e1c19ec9262116aa2fa357-kix.5b3dpx8k4cq